# npm auth for publishing the public @lesto/* surface (see RELEASING.md).
# Reads the token from the NPM_TOKEN env var — no literal secret is committed.
# Used by `changeset publish` (`bun run release`) both locally (export NPM_TOKEN=…)
# and in CI (the NPM_TOKEN repo secret, via .github/workflows/release.yml).
# Harmless when NPM_TOKEN is unset: it expands to empty and public installs still resolve.
//registry.npmjs.org/:_authToken=${NPM_TOKEN}
